Class jdbcpostgreSQL

java.lang.Object
jdbcpostgreSQL
public class jdbcpostgreSQL
extends java.lang.Object
Commands to run this script This will compile all java files in this directory javac *.java This command tells the file where to find the postgres jar which it needs to execute postgres commands, then executes the code Windows: java -cp ".;postgresql-42.2.8.jar" jdbcpostgreSQL Mac/Linux: java -cp ".:postgresql-42.2.8.jar" jdbcpostgreSQL MAKE SURE YOU ARE ON VPN or TAMU WIFI TO ACCESS DATABASE
